dataset.name: NYMEX Silver, December 2018 (SIZ2018)
dataset.description:
Contract Size: 5,000 troy ounces

Deliverable Good: Silver delivered under this contract shall assay to a minimum of 999 fineness.

Tick Size: Outright transactions including EFP: $0.005 per troy ounce. Straddle or spread transactions and settlement prices: $0.001 per troy ounce.

Pricing Unit: U.S. Dollars and Cents

Columns: Open, High, Low, Settle, Volume, Previous Day Open Interest. Note that Open Interest is always reported for the previous trading day, to avoid lookahead bias.
